txt.en: You have destroyed the cruel masks that Orcs and goblins hung in Mudmul-charâf.
Crude masks in Mudmul-charâf have been hung in mockery of the statues of the dwarves, gaping in their cruel Orkish laughter.

Crude masks hewn and hung by the enemy can be found in Mudmul-charâf in the north-west halls of Zelem-melek.\n\nYou should destroy the crude masks, for they mock the fine statues made by the dwarves of old.
